Altmobile Helps You Simplify The Process of Phone Ownership

Altmobile is a credit financing platform powered by the 
Alternative Bank which provides financing for mobile devices. 
The company’s processes are defined to fit into the lifestyle 
and earning patterns of its target customers. 
Altmobile is looking to build a landing page and web 
application that informs customers of its various propositions 
and guides them through how to apply. This website should 
align with its brand values while informing and engaging the 
web audience effectively.
